Texts.Chs: 一些看不见的敌手破坏了我们唯一可用的太空飞船。其他人怀疑我们的上级军官，他似乎很满足于被困在这个星球上。他坐在那里盯着他的图表，试图给人一种他知道该做什么的印象。可他不会。
Texts.Eng: Some unseen antagonist has sabotaged our only working space craft. The others suspect our superior officer, who seems pretty content to be trapped on this planet. He sits there staring at his charts, trying to give the impression he knows what to do. He doesn't.
